Recommends: dino-im-plugins
Description: Modern XMPP ("Jabber") instant messaging client
 Dino is a modern XMPP instant messaging client for Linux, built with GTK4.
 It features a clean interface and supports:
  - One-on-one and group chats
  - End-to-end encryption (OMEMO, OpenPGP)
  - File transfers
  - Voice/video calls (via GStreamer)
  - Message corrections and reactions
  - Read receipts (XEP-0333)
  - Text zoom feature
 .
 This fork includes additional features:
  - AI-generated text zoom (Ctrl++, Ctrl+-, Ctrl+0)
  - Visible read receipt indicators
  - Resizable sidebar
 .
 This package provides the main Dino application.

Package: dino-im-plugins
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         dino-im (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Optional plugins for Dino IM
 This package contains optional plugins for Dino IM including:
  - OMEMO encryption
  - OpenPGP encryption
  - Voice/video calls (RTP)
  - ICE for P2P communication
  - HTTP file upload
